## 2026-04-03 - Token editor save failure has no retry affordance
- Added `saveRetryArgs: [boolean, boolean] | null` state to track whether the current error is from a server/network save failure (retryable) vs a validation failure (not retryable). Set in the `handleSave` catch block; cleared at save start and on validation errors.
