- Also fixed a pre-existing build-breaking bug: `allTokensFlat` was declared twice in `TokenGeneratorDialogProps` interface and twice in the component destructuring, causing esbuild to fail with "cannot be bound multiple times". Removed the duplicate interface entry and destructuring binding.

