## 2026-04-03 - BatchEditor has no bulk copy-to-set operation
- Added "Copy to set" alongside the existing "Move" button in BatchEditor. Copy preserves originals in the source set and overwrites any existing tokens at the same paths in the target set.
- Added `batchCopyTokens` method to `token-store.ts` — reads tokens from source set, deep-clones them, writes to target set (overwrite), saves only the target. No delete from source.
- Added `POST /api/tokens/:set/batch-copy` route in `tokens.ts` — snapshots target before/after for operation log, returns `{ ok, copied, operationId }`.

