- **App.tsx** (split-view section): Changed `onNavigateToToken` to call `setPreviewingToken` (focus token in preview pane) instead of navigating the list. Added `focusedToken={previewingToken}`, `pathToSet`, `onClearFocus`, and `onEditToken` (which collapses split view and opens editor sidebar) to the PreviewPanel call. Updated split-view TokenList `highlightedToken` to also reflect `previewingToken?.path`.

